skdetail:

Invocation Name: basketball gym sounds
des:
Calling all basketball fans! Basketball Gym Sounds give you the familiar sounds of a friendly pick-up basketball game being played at an indoor gym.

The familiar screech as players pivot quickly on the court. The repeated thump of the dribble. Basketball Gym Sounds is great for masking distracting noises by providing you with mild background noise.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
